Hierarchy

  • UrlParameters

Indexable

[widgetId: string]: string

this is for make widget to support custom URL parameters. the suggest pattern is: ?widget1=p1=v1,p2=v2, but every widget can define it's own pattern

Optional data_id

data_id: string
  • Defined in jimu-core/lib/types/url-parameters.ts:50

the data select, use this format: dsId:selectId the select id can be:

  • <id1+id2+id3> this means the id must not contain "+"

Optional data_index

data_index: string
  • Defined in jimu-core/lib/types/url-parameters.ts:42

the data select, use this format: dsId:selectIndex the select index can be:

  • , means index is selected.
  • <i1+i2+i3>, means index <i1, i2, i3> is selected.
  • , means index is selected.
  • +, means index and is selected.

Optional draft

draft: string
  • Defined in jimu-core/lib/types/url-parameters.ts:67

by default, app will load config from item data. But before publish, the item data is empty, we can set draft=1 to load config from item resource draft = <true | 1>

Optional layouts

layouts: string
